  "text": [
    "The whole ball",
    "of who we are",
    "presses into",
    "the green baize",
    "at a single tiny",
    "spot. An aural",
    "track of crackle",
    "betrays our passage",
    "through the",
    "fibrous jungle.",
    "It\u2019s hot and",
    "desperate. Insects",
    "spring out of it.",
    "The pressure is",
    "intense, and the",
    "sense that we\u2019ve",
    "lost proportion.",
    "As though bringing",
    "too much to bear",
    "too locally were",
    "our decision."
  ],
  "title": "A Ball Rolls on a Point",
  "year": ""
}